text:
I have an Ambiance playlist playing on spotify right now.
It decided to make Peacock sounds. Que lould squarking
Peacocks are Absolutely *not* what you want to hear in peaceful ambiance.
My old univerity had peacocks roaming the grounds, they are also not what you want to hear when you are trying to do an exam.
